summary: This is an FBI administrative memorandum requesting the closure of the obstruction of justice case against Alfredo Rodriguez. It states that all investigative and prosecutorial issues have been resolved.

events.title: Request for Case Closure
events.description: An FBI memorandum is drafted requesting the administrative closure of the obstruction of justice case against Alfredo Rodriguez, citing that all issues have been resolved.

keyFacts: The FBI is requesting administrative closure of the obstruction of justice case against Alfredo Rodriguez.
The document states that all investigative and prosecutorial issues in the case have been resolved.
The case is identified by the ID number 72-MM-113327 and was pending at the time of the memo.
